        </div>
        <h4 class="pillar__title">Observability Infrastructure</h4>
        <ul class="pillar__features">
          <li class="pillar__feature">Activation caching across timesteps and modules</li>
          <li class="pillar__feature">Saliency maps over trajectories</li>
          <li class="pillar__feature">Surprise detection and belief tracking</li>
